title: God Eater 2 - PSP [Japanese - Full game]
description:
Hello, this is my first upload.
Anyway, this is the japanese PSP version of God Eater 2, it was hard to find since it just came out so I thought I could share it.

For those searching for the Gintama outfits, they are unlocked after the tutorial section in the store (buying the costume unlocks the hairstyle).
